proof_script:
lemma list_nth_append3: assumes h1:"\<not> i < Suc (length x)" and "i - Suc (length x) < Suc (length y)" shows "(a # y) ! (i - Suc (length x)) = (b # x @ a # y) ! i"
using h1
by (auto simp: nth_append)
